description:
Billy Bob Thornton is an Academy Award–winning actor, filmmaker, and musician. He currently stars as Tommy Norris in the Paramount+ series “Landman” and is the lead singer of The Boxmasters. Season two of “Landman” premieres on November 16. “Pepper Tree Hill,” the latest album from The Boxmasters, is available now.
